<topic template="Default" modified="2020-06-15T16:58:28.233+03:00" lasteditedby="User1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Updating</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Updating</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">When a new version is ready, it has to be published to</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> Components Gallery</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> again. The new </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">version</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> number should be set in the component&apos;s </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">package.json</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> file before publishing in order to make each version of the component available. Thus, the component from the previous version can still be available for installation. We recommended to follow the rules and requirements of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="weblink" href="https://semver.org/" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">semantic versioning</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> that dictate the way version numbers are assigned and incremented.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">The component can be removed from the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">Components Gallery</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">. Just select the component and press the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">Remove from eWizard</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> button:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><image src="Screen-Shot-2018-05-31-at-10.32.30-AM.png" scale="42.67%" width="1177" height="155" padding="0 0 1 0" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:12pt;"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">If the further installation of the component has to be stopped, it can be deleted from the Components Gallery. This action is available via the Components Gallery interface and for the component publisher only. Select the component in the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">Components Gallery</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">, open details and press </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">Delete</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> (below the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true">Remove from eWizard</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#424242;" translate="true"> button):</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.25; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><image src="Screen-Shot-2018-05-31-at-10.32.15-AM.png" scale="37.07%" width="1031" height="216" padding="0 0 1 0" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:12pt;"></image></para>
  </body>
